argain.", "words": [{"w": "He", "s": 88.7, "e": 89.32}, {"w": "has", "s": 89.32, "e": 89.5}, {"w": "a", "s": 89.5, "e": 89.64}, {"w": "keen", "s": 89.64, "e": 89.86}, {"w": "eye", "s": 89.86, "e": 90.26}, {"w": "for", "s": 90.26, "e": 90.52}, {"w": "a", "s": 90.52, "e": 90.68}, {"w": "bargain.", "s": 90.68, "e": 91.0}]}, {"start": 94.02, "end": 97.38, "text": "When I was young, my sister always teased me.", "words": [{"w": "When", "s": 94.02, "e": 94.64}, {"w": "I", "s": 94.64, "e": 94.8}, {"w": "was", "s": 94.8, "e": 94.98}, {"w": "young,", "s": 94.98, "e": 95.32}, {"w": "my", "s": 95.68, "e": 95.82}, {"w": "sister", "s": 95.82, "e": 96.12}, {"w": "always", "s": 96.12, "e": 96.7}, {"w": "teased", "s": 96.7, "e": 97.16}, {"w": "me.", "s": 97.16, "e": 97.38}]}, {"start": 100.52, "end": 104.76, "text": "Most importantly, you must ask him about his plans for the future.", "words": [{"w": "Most", "s": 100.52, "e": 101.0}, {"w": "importantly,", "s": 101.0, "e": 101.54}, {"w": "you", "s": 102.18, "e": 102.36}, {"w": "must", "s": 102.36, "e": 102.54}, {"w": "ask", "s": 102.54, "e": 102.9}, {"w": "him", "s": 102.9, "e": 103.14}, {"w": "about", "s": 103.14, "e": 103.36}, {"w": "his", "s": 103.36, "e": 103.6}, {"w": "plans", "s": 103.6, "e": 104.04}, {"w": "for", "s": 104.04, "e": 104.32}, {"w": "the", "s": 104.32, "e": 104.44}, {"w": "future.", "s": 104.44, "e": 104.76}]}]